&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Synchronicity Care Ltd are seeking to recruit an experienced procurement professional into the role of Senior Procurement Officer within a very busy Procurement Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you have a sound understanding of procurement law (PCR 15), experience in undertaking complex tenders, a proven record of establishing strong and supportive professional relationships and a genuine desire to achieve continuous improvement, both personally and across a wider team, then we would encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you would like further information about this role please contact Stephanie Brennan, Head of Procurement at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Stephanie.brennan2@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; or 07917 091097&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
